com.bigdata.rawstore

Class IPSOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • com.bigdata.rawstore.IPSOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PSOutputStream

    public abstract class IPSOutputStream
extends OutputStream
    This class provides a stream-based allocation mechanism.

    The intention is that an IPSOutputStream (PS for PerSistent) is returned by a storage service to which data can be written. When all data has been written the address from which to retriev an InputStream can be requested.

    Author:
    Martyn Cutcher
